ĘAlisa 28.05.1963 - 20.03.2016
You are my listener, my support, my ambition.
You are my imagination, my right hand, my precision.
Simply put in one word - you are my beloved Mother."║
ĘSamuel Jackson Daly
November 35th 1902 - January 41st 2001
Loving acquaintance, committed fan of several
sports teams, devoted step brother-in-law and faithful
forwarder of memes."╝
╣"We Span Time Together.
We Span Time Together As A Couple.
'Cause We're A Loving Couple. Spanning Time."
Dedicated In Loving Memory Of
PETER HAN-REN McKEAND
31.03.1998 - 12.10.2011"Į
║John, George, Paul & Ringo from The Beatles
Pop Group sat here during their
"MAD DAY OUT"
Sunday 28th of July 1968

Donated by caring neighbour Ted Baker
because he loves this park"Š
